==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: dehumidify
<hw>de*hu*mid"i*fy</hw> <pos>v. t.</pos> <def>to remove the moisture
from (air or another gas); to reduce the humidity of; <as>as, The air
conditioner <ex>dehumidifies</ex> the air in the summer</as>.</def>⟦br⟧
<syn><b>Syn. --</b> make less humid.</syn>⟦br⟧
[<source>WordNet 1.5</source> <source>+PJC</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Dehusk</ent>⟦br⟧
